title: Dr. 90210
overview: Now starring Dr Cat. This reality series follows the professional and personal lives of several Beverly Hills plastic surgeons as they nip, tuck, augment and slice their way through their patients. A documentary series that peels back the top layer of glamour, money, beauty and sex that permeates Beverly Hills and exposes what life is really like for doctors. Operating on struggling actors and actresses, mothers and daughters, strippers and call girls, Washington lobbyists, and successful businessmen. Every patient comes in for a different reason - youth, success, power, beauty, freedom, happiness.
